  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5228903">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5228903/" class="title-link">我们应该拥有怎样的明天</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5228903"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3010816/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3010816-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3010816/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">余味清欢</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-12-25"
      class="main-meta">2011-12-25 11:59:32</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5228903_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我在2011年的平安夜看完了杨恒均先生的《家国天下》，这是我看过的唯一一本能用最通俗易懂的语言把民主政治讲得那么透彻明了的书。他的文字亲切平和，剖析的事例是每天都发生在你我身边的，而所要表达的意思观念关乎我们每个人的未来。我愿向每一位关心国家和自己明天的人大力...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5228903_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5228903_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










